io.smudgr.engine.param

Class Parametric

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.smudgr.engine.param.Parametric
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ProjectItem, ReflectableType
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Rack, Smudge, SmudgeComponent

    public abstract class Parametric
extends java.lang.Object
implements ProjectItem
    The abstract Parametric class defines generic behavior for ProjectItem implementations that contain and use Parameter parameters.
